{
  "texts": [
    "To ensure that the results were accurate and interpretable, we performed a manual review of both the identified topics and the corresponding representative publications.",
    "This process involved three experts who conducted a qualitative assessment to verify that the topics were coherent and meaningful, in line with recent BERTopic studies (Douglas et al., 2024; Wang et al., 2023).",
    "The experts evaluated the keywords associated with each topic and reviewed the representative publications by analyzing abstracts, titles, and, when necessary, the full texts.",
    "Additionally, probability values and citation counts were used to select the top three representative articles for each topic.",
    "To ensure the reliability of our process, we used a straightforward scoring system to evaluate each topic's relevance."
  ]
}